    "description": "A new take on the <strong>Infinite Runner,</strong> now in <strong>VR</strong>. <br>Dodge, Jump, and Vault with both hands as you make your way through infinite obstacles and Zombies. <br>Unlock more weapons to help you progress further. <br><br>How far will you go? <br><br>Maps are randomly generated, so you'll get a different layout each time. <br>The only thing you can count on, is eventual death.<br><br>Please Join Us On Discord, to make this a better game:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298140/extras/dbb4953e33b43d5df5a6e32d9d7acb75.avif?t=1688056709\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><br><br><br>It’s VR, designed for full room-scale/standing tracking with motion controllers. Simple controls allow seated, or less mobile players.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>To Jump, Press B<br></li><li>If you have a bad back, press A to Duck.<br></li><li>If you don't have room to dodge, use the Thumbstick.<br></li><li>If you can't swing your arms up and down, press both jump buttons to vault.<br></li><li>If you can't swing your arms around..... don't select the melee weapons.</li></ul><br><strong><u>The Game has been played on Valve Index, HTC Vive, and Quest 2 (including Virtual Desktop)</u></strong><br><i>Trailer1 song adrenaline by romanov_studio   5419</i><br><i>Trailer2 song midnight-club by musical_bakery   5419</i>",
